743
00:47:01,040 --> 00:47:02,439
Ben?

744
00:47:03,680 --> 00:47:05,398
Are you okay in there?

745
00:47:05,840 --> 00:47:07,114
Earth to Ben.

746
00:47:07,840 --> 00:47:09,114
Yeah.

747
00:47:09,400 --> 00:47:12,437
- You sure everything's all right?
