00:49:03,200 --> 00:49:05,316
Blood type, DNA.

772
00:49:05,520 --> 00:49:07,476
Well, the Army never put one in me.

773
00:49:11,160 --> 00:49:13,310
That you know of, man.

774
00:49:15,720 --> 00:49:17,392
That you know of.

775
00:49:27,680 --> 00:49:29,432
